00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:21,760
(In the fourth year of Chuigong's reign,)

2
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:24,680
(Wu Zetian's ambition
to ascend the throne)

3
00:00:24,680 --> 00:00:26,320
(plunges the court and the realm
into great fear.)

4
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,240
(Rumors are rampant,)

5
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:30,040
(and strange events
occur in succession.)

6
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:33,760
(Word has it that an omen
appeared in the Luo River.)

7
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,080
(A divine stone emerged.)

8
00:00:36,080 --> 00:00:37,960
(It was inscribed with the words,)

9
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:41,080
("The Holy Empress Descends to Rule,
The Empire Shall Prosper.")

10
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:43,120
(The Heavenly Empress is overjoyed.)

11
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:44,080
(An auspicious date is chosen,)

12
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:46,200
(and an altar is erected
by the Luo River)

13
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,480
(to proclaim the Heavenly Mandate
to the realm.)

14
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,800
(She then orders
the Directorate of Astronomy)

15
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:52,320
(to guard the divine stone)

16
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:53,960
(for the ceremony.)

17
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,860
(Directorate of Astronomy)

18
00:00:56,900 --> 00:00:59,890
(The night before the Heavenly Mandate
Enthronement Ceremony, early Xu Hour)

19
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,040
(The Empire Shall Proper)
(On the eve of the ceremony,)

20
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:11,600
(42 court ladies died mysteriously.)

21
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:13,420
(Their deaths are bizarre.)

22
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,160
(A deeper mist of mystery)

23
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,720
(shrouds the Tang realm.)

24
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:21,260
=The Tang Mist S1=

25
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:24,040
Something terrible has happened
at the Directorate of Astronomy!

26
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:45,420
=Episode 1=

27
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:50,380
(Three days before the ceremony,
Shendu City)

28
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,200
Your Highness,

29
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:55,080
(Li Youdao, Wu Zetian's trusted minister)
These two women, one black and one yellow,

30
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,480
represent Heaven and Earth.

31
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,760
The other four

32
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,080
represent the four seasons.

33
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,640
Behind them sit 12 more,

34
00:03:00,650 --> 00:03:02,290
representing
the twelve hours of the day.

35
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,880
Another 24

36
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,880
represent the 24 solar terms.

37
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,800
Together, they make 42 court ladies.

38
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:11,240
Among them, 28 represent

39
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,840
the constellations of the heavens.

40
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:15,800
13 represent

41
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,600
the 13 circuits of the Tang realm.

42
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,960
And the final one represents

43
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,640
the seat of rule over all under Heaven,

44
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,080
Shendu City.

45
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:24,680
Their birth dates

46
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:26,120
and natal charts

47
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,680
were carefully selected.

48
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,680
With them offering worship here,

49
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:32,280
the Heavenly Mandate
will surely shine ever brighter,

50
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,520
(The Holy Empress Descends to Rule)
blessed with greater favor from Heaven.

51
00:03:33,530 --> 00:03:34,640
The Heavenly Mandate
Enthronement Ceremony

52
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,120
three days from now

53
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,560
shall proceed without fail.

54
00:03:47,340 --> 00:03:54,380
(Wu Zetian, Heavenly Empress)

55
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,360
Li Youdao,

56
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,400
the arrangement

57
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:01,240
is indeed thorough and meticulous.

58
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,400
It's commendable.

59
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,200
Thank you, Your Highness.

60
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,680
In ancient times, Divine Emperor Fuxi

61
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,520
received the Luo Chart
from the Luo River

62
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,960
and founded the Xia Dynasty.

63
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,480
And now, Your Highness

64
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:15,040
has received the Heavenly Mandate
from the Luo River

65
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,440
to rule over the Nine Provinces.

66
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:18,640
Recently,

67
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,400
I've observed the signs in the heavens.

68
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:21,680
I reckon

69
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,400
(The Empire Shall Prosper)
whoever obtains this white stone

70
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:26,240
should be honored
with the title of Divine Emperor.

71
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,520
I'm aware

72
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,920
of your sincerity.

73
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,280
You have put great thought

74
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:36,040
into this.

75
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:45,300
(Late Xu Hour)

76
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:49,000
Something terrible has happened
at the Directorate of Astronomy!

77
00:04:49,010 --> 00:04:50,680
Something terrible has happened
at the Directorate of Astronomy!

78
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,520
Quick!

79
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,280
Quick!

80
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,120
Move aside! Move!

81
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,080
Big or small?

82
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:03,000
(Duan Shisi, subordinate of Di Renjie)

83
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,480
(Once served as a military scout)
Small.

84
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,240
(Sharp ears, swift feet)
Move aside!

85
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:07,840
Small!

86
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:08,680
Something has happened.

87
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,820
(Lin Buyan,
beloved disciple of Di Renjie)

88
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:29,180
(Skilled with the staff and portraiture,
uses paintings to identify criminals)

89
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:36,600
Di.

90
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,120
(The Holy Empress Descends to Rule, The Empire Shall Prosper)
Just as you predicted.

91
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,600
Something has happened
at the Directorate of Astronomy.

92
00:05:43,540 --> 00:05:45,580
(Di Renjie, courtesy name Huaiying)

93
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:48,460
(Upright and incorruptible,
brilliant at solving cases)

94
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:51,120
Master, we're still under house arrest
by Her Highness.

95
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,560
House arrest is trivial.

96
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,400
The real problem is
if the crime scene gets tampered with.

97
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,960
We must get there before anyone else.

98
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:56,840
No worries, Di.

99
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,640
The messenger's horse

100
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:01,120
(Zetian Gate)
can't outrun me.

101
00:06:01,130 --> 00:06:03,310
The Court of Judicial Review is here
by imperial order to investigate.

102
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:05,680
Everyone else, stand aside.

103
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:06,800
Sir.

104
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:09,000
Officials of the Court
of the Judicial Review, you're fast indeed.

105
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,000
Official Di, aren't you under house arrest
by Her Highness?

106
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,080
Didn't you see the token?

107
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,520
This way, please.

108
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:26,960
Duan,

109
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,960
guard the door.

110
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,720
(The joints)

111
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:04,280
(are rigid.)

112
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:06,320
(Estimated time of death
is around 16 hours ago.)

113
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,080
(Time of death)

114
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,680
(is late Xu Hour last night.)

115
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:22,520
(The lips are dark purple.)

116
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,080
(Blood from the mouth and eyes.)

117
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:27,200
(Red blotches across the skin.)

118
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,840
(These are signs of poisoning.)

119
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,840
Who has the audacity

120
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,400
to intrude upon the crime scene?

121
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,280
Duan.

122
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,760
(Xue Huaiyi, formerly a monk)
Xue Huaiyi?

123
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,300
(Favored aide of Wu Zetian)

124
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,720
They are officials
from the Court of Judicial Review.

125
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,510
They claim they're here by imperial order
to investigate.

126
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:36,920
Oh?

127
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,280
Why have I heard nothing

128
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,960
about this case being transferred
to the Court of Judicial Review?

129
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,520
Keep the case records safe.

130
00:08:48,530 --> 00:08:50,150
This matter is
of significant importance.

131
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,990
The order must've come
directly from Her Highness.

132
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:54,200
Official Di carries
the Heavenly Empress's token.

133
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,400
Sir,

134
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:57,880
please show your badge
and clear up the misunderstanding.

135
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,280
I doubt he can.

136
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,240
Di Renjie.

137
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,360
Whether I can show it or not

138
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,920
is a matter for the outer court.

139
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,990
It has nothing to do
with an inner court servant.

140
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:10,080
You must be exhausted
from serving at Her Highness's side.

141
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,080
Why trouble yourself by coming here?

142
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:15,240
You were punished

143
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,800
for scolding Zhang Guangfu.

144
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,200
As someone under punishment,

145
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,240
you should be staying confined.

146
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:24,200
Are you not afraid

147
00:09:24,210 --> 00:09:26,130
Her Highness will punish you
even more severely?

148
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,080
Go on.

149
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,360
Show us your token.

150
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:41,420
(Earth Four)

151
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,360
Earth Room Number Four.

152
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:46,600
Using a door key as an official token?

153
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:49,560
Have you mistaken the Directorate
of Astronomy for an inn?

154
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,480
Send them out.

155
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,760
Master,

156
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,600
why didn't you let me beat up
that fake monk?

157
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,880
If not for his slander,

158
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,400
you never would've been confined.

159
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,920
What a disgraceful monk.

160
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:01,870
There's no need
to waste your strength on him.

161
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,600
Di,

162
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,840
did you discover something?

163
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,120
Those 42 court ladies

164
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,520
died from poison.

165
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:09,640
This poison brings great pleasure,
causing the victim to die smiling.

166
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:12,110
Its formula is reserved exclusively
for the imperial family.

167
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:12,960
Are you saying

168
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,360
this is an internal royal conflict?

169
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,080
For the Heavenly Mandate
Enthronement Ceremony,

170
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,000
these 42 court ladies

171
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,840
had remained inside the bureau
for two days.

172
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,720
None of them left even once.

173
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,960
This poison takes five hours
to take effect.

174
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,080
Judging by their time of death,

175
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,440
the poison must've been administered
yesterday

176
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:29,230
between the late Wei Hour
and early Shen hour.

177
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,560
Look into the visitor records

178
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,790
of the Directorate of Astronomy
from yesterday.

179
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:33,080
I'm heading to
the Imperial Academy of Medicine

180
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,200
to see who obtained

181
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,320
the imperial poison formula.

182
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:35,920
Understood.

183
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:39,280
Sir,

184
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,600
(Imperial Academy of Medicine)
these are the recent visitor records.

185
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,720
Please have a look.

186
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,560
Liu Wuzhi?

187
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,800
Why did he come here?

188
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:51,960
To obtain Frost Flame.

189
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,840
Frost Flame.

190
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,600
Di,

191
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,920
Liu Wuzhi has been arrested.

192
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,680
Not only did he visit
the Imperial Academy of Medicine,

193
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:05,120
but he also went to the Directorate
of Astronomy before the murders.

194
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:07,440
Liu Wuzhi is a loyal supporter
of the Li family's rightful rule

195
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,520
who opposes the Heavenly Empress.

196
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:10,960
So he poisoned the court ladies
to sabotage the ceremony.

197
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,440
He's been thrown into prison.

198
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,320
(But this poison)

199
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,280
(isn't Frost Flame.)

200
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:23,920
After investigation,

201
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,760
the 42 court ladies

202
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:28,280
are confirmed
to have died from Frost Flame.

203
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:31,680
Its formula is kept confidential by
the Imperial Academy of Medicine.

204
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:34,640
According to the visitor records,

205
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:37,080
Liu Wuzhi was the only person

206
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,600
authorized to obtain it.

207
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,880
Besides, guards from
the Directorate of Astronomy

208
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,240
and Li Youdao both testified

209
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:44,280
that during the late Wei hour
of the day of the incident,

210
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:44,840
Liu Wuzhi

211
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:47,120
dismissed everyone from the bureau

212
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,560
under the pretense of praying for
His Majesty.

213
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:52,800
Only he and the court ladies
were inside the hall at that time.

214
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,520
The Heavenly Mandate
Enthronement Ceremony is approaching,

215
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:58,240
yet Liu Wuzhi brazenly committed
such an atrocity.

216
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,480
(Liu Wuzhi, Grand Chancellor)
The witnesses and evidence are conclusive.

217
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:03,680
He has now been imprisoned

218
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,200
and will be executed tomorrow

219
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:07,040
in accordance with the law.

220
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:13,520
Liu Wuzhi has crossed the line.

221
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,440
Though

222
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,400
I am compassionate,

223
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,640
I cannot tolerate such evil.

224
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:22,880
In court, the loyal and treacherous
are now clearly revealed.

225
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:26,680
This shall be a warning to all of you.

226
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:29,000
Do not follow in his footsteps.

227
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:34,080
The Heavenly Empress is wise.

228
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:36,160
His Majesty is wise.

229
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,480
Your Highness,

230
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:40,760
I, Di Renjie, have something to report.

231
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,120
Di Renjie,

232
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,800
does the punishment I imposed

233
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:50,480
mean nothing

234
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,120
to you?

235
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,160
Forgive me, Your Highness.

236
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:56,080
This matter is
of significant importance.

237
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,200
I dared not delay in the slightest.

238
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,440
Huaiying,

239
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,840
rise.

240
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,520
Thank you, Your Highness.

241
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,560
I acted without permission

242
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:24,440
and investigated the deaths
of the 42 court ladies.

243
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:26,400
I also went to the prison
without permission

244
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:28,400
to meet with Grand Chancellor Liu Wuzhi.

245
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,400
But I dare say with certainty,

246
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:32,640
Liu Wuzhi is innocent.

247
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,760
Are you questioning

248
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:37,040
my judgment?

249
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,520
I beg Your Highness's pardon,

250
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,840
but I ask to speak
in Liu Wuzhi's defense.

251
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:42,360
Speak.

252
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,680
Liu Wuzhi is well-versed in medicine.

253
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:47,080
He knew the heat poison in Frost Flame.

254
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,480
If used in proper dosage,

255
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:50,480
it could treat
His Majesty's cold illness.

256
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:53,080
Hence, he went to the Imperial Academy
of Medicine to obtain Frost Flame.

257
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:55,440
I intended to test the medicine myself,

258
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:57,760
hoping to ease His Majesty's suffering.

259
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:59,040
I didn't expect this

260
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:01,720
to be the excuse to frame me.

261
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,640
That's Liu Wuzhi's side of the story.

262
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:05,000
Do you have proof?

263
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,480
(The Holy Empress Descends to Rule)
The key

264
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,600
is the timing.

265
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:10,800
Frost Flame takes eight hours
to take effect.

266
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,920
It would've needed to be administered
around noon.

267
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:14,320
But at that time,

268
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,960
Liu Wuzhi wasn't in
the Directorate of Astronomy.

269
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,800
Huaiying, are you suggesting

270
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:21,360
the real poisoner was someone else?

271
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:23,520
Duan, Buyan.

272
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,920
I'll write out a prescription.

273
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:26,080
You two investigate

274
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:27,520
and find out
who was compounding this medicine.

275
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,600
We've checked

276
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:30,280
every apothecary in the nearby ward.

277
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,440
Does he look like this?

278
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:37,360
Nice skill, sir.

279
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:39,000
It's exactly the same.

280
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:42,000
Li Youdao?

281
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:44,400
Within a single night,

282
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:46,080
Li Youdao visited apothecaries
all across Shendu

283
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:48,440
and gathered the ingredients
for another poison.

284
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:51,280
This poison takes five hours to kill.

285
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,880
The victims die smiling.

286
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:53,720
This is the true poison

287
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:56,160
behind the deaths of the 42 court ladies.

288
00:14:56,920 --> 00:14:58,440
Begonia Red.

289
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:00,680
Your Highness,

290
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:02,560
I suppose you remember this poison.

291
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,320
Thirteen years ago,

292
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,640
Crown Prince Li Hong

293
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:11,440
was murdered with it.

294
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,680
After this incident,

295
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:17,040
I'm facing condemnation from the people.

296
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,640
I was ordered to investigate
the case of the Crown Prince

297
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:21,600
in secret.

298
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,880
The culprit has been executed.

299
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:25,440
Since the poison formula belongs
exclusively to the imperial family,

300
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:27,720
how did Li Youdao obtain it

301
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,600
without going through
the Imperial Academy of Medicine?

302
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,080
(The Holy Empress Descends to Rule)
I reckon whoever obtains the white stone...

303
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,720
Li Youdao has always

304
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,760
openly supported Your Highness.

305
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:36,360
Should be honored
with the title of the Divine Emperor.

306
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:40,120
Begonia Red has always been
a painful wound in your heart.

307
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:41,320
Without permission,

308
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:44,280
how would Li Youdao dare

309
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:46,280
rehash the past?

310
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,360
Furthermore,

311
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,880
you have long been at odds
with Liu Wuzhi.

312
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:54,520
Official Liu,

313
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:56,240
why did you go to
the Directorate of Astronomy?

314
00:15:58,080 --> 00:16:00,600
You should ask your Heavenly Empress.

315
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:03,040
You suddenly summoned him
to go to the Directorate of Astronomy

316
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:04,520
to pray for His Majesty.

317
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:06,280
It was an unusual order.

318
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:07,600
Forgive my ignorance,

319
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,240
but it aroused my suspicions.

320
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,280
So by your reasoning,

321
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,440
I appear

322
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,680
highly suspicious.

323
00:16:16,680 --> 00:16:17,920
If I meant to frame him,

324
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,960
why bother

325
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:23,120
replacing Frost Flame

326
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:25,240
with Begonia Red?

327
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:27,200
Apparently,

328
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:29,000
Liu Wuzhi was only the first step.

329
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:31,120
Once something happened at the ceremony,

330
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,800
it should've been kept secret.

331
00:16:32,800 --> 00:16:34,180
Instead, the signal drums were sounded.

332
00:16:34,180 --> 00:16:36,640
- The entire city heard about it.
-Something happened at the Directorate of Astronomy!

333
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:37,760
(Zetian Gate)
The Directorate of Astronomy is a restricted area.

334
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,800
Even if I had wanted to sneak in,

335
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,520
without Li Youdao's consent,

336
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,760
I would've never gotten inside.

337
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,640
He let me in on purpose,

338
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,840
so I would notice

339
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:47,920
something was wrong.

340
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,480
Am I right,

341
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,280
Your Highness?

342
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:56,280
Just because I call you "Huaiying"

343
00:16:57,040 --> 00:16:59,080
doesn't mean you can forget your place.

344
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,240
You're using this matter

345
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:06,360
to test where the court officials stand.

346
00:17:07,320 --> 00:17:08,680
Those who stay silent
in their own defense

347
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:11,000
are aligned with you.

348
00:17:11,360 --> 00:17:12,960
Anyone who dares speak out

349
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:16,040
may well become the next Liu Wuzhi.

350
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,800
Your Highness,

351
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:20,360
to eliminate your enemies,

352
00:17:21,360 --> 00:17:22,560
the cost

353
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,160
is far too great.

354
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:26,040
Well, well, Di Renjie.

355
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,080
Whether it is a road

356
00:17:28,080 --> 00:17:29,160
or an abyss

357
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,040
before you,

358
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:34,200
you'd better look carefully.

359
00:17:38,360 --> 00:17:39,160
Your Highness,

360
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:41,000
my life and death

361
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,320
have always rested upon

362
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,440
a single thought from you.

363
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,760
But today,

364
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:48,080
I beg Your Highness

365
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:50,200
to remember my past service

366
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,400
and spare my life.

367
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:59,720
And if I insist?

368
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:04,120
I never earned my rank and title

369
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:06,960
for wealth or glory,

370
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,280
not for fame and power.

371
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:11,240
When I vowed to serve the people
all my life,

372
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:13,760
I wasn't only

373
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:14,840
paying lip service.

374
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:18,040
If Your Highness insists on
taking that step,

375
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:19,960
then the way under your feet
will be paved with blood and lives.

376
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,760
And I, Di Renjie,

377
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,160
would rather die in chains

378
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,760
than serve an unrighteous ruler.

379
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:38,440
I await

380
00:18:39,360 --> 00:18:40,720
Your Highness's judgment.

381
00:18:58,720 --> 00:18:59,680
Di Renjie,

382
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,520
I'm a man of loyalty and integrity.

383
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,440
You needn't beg for my life.

384
00:19:07,560 --> 00:19:08,600
I wasn't begging for your sake.

385
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:11,280
I was begging for
the loyal ministers of Tang.

386
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:18,240
This is the prison.

387
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:21,560
There's no need for you
to keep pretending

388
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:24,440
in front of a man who's about to die.

389
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:33,920
For the loyal ministers of Tang?

390
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,240
What a joke.

391
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,440
You should concern yourself instead

392
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,920
with serving your Heavenly Empress well.

393
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:48,240
Your Excellency,

394
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:51,280
I know the kind of man you are.

395
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,560
You never wished to be a servant
of imperial power.

396
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:57,280
You only wished to be
a servant of the people.

397
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,960
And I

398
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:01,080
am the same.

399
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,320
A servant of the people...

400
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,440
Many new counties are established
throughout Jiangnan.

401
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:43,280
Di Renjie is appointed
Imperial Commissioner of Jiangnan

402
00:20:43,320 --> 00:20:44,560
with authority over
promotions and dismissals

403
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:47,160
to inspect the Jiangnan Circuit
on my behalf.

404
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:48,640
Master,

405
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,160
you offended Her Highness,

406
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,400
yet you still got promoted?

407
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:53,360
Promoted, you say?

408
00:20:53,360 --> 00:20:54,320
You truly

409
00:20:54,800 --> 00:20:56,280
are clueless.

410
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:58,480
Put nicely, he's
the Imperial Commissioner of Jiangnan.

411
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,320
Put bluntly,

412
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:01,320
it's exile.

413
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:03,920
Official Di,

414
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:07,000
did my Godfather leave any word?

415
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:09,280
Only one.

416
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:11,480
Do not think of revenge.

417
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:17,420
(Chu Qinglan, goddaughter of Liu Wuzhi,
skilled at medicine and poison)

418
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:18,560
I, Chu Qinglan,

419
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:19,840
am skilled in both medicine and poison.

420
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,000
I can be of use.

421
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:22,240
Starting today,

422
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,280
I wish to follow you, Official Di.

423
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,000
That girl...

424
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,600
Official Liu's surname is Liu.

425
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:31,200
Why is hers Chu?

426
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:32,000
Goddaughter.

427
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,320
Adopted daughter, you know?

428
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:34,520
You really don't understand anything,
do you?

429
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:36,720
Time to depart.

430
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:40,160
Depart!

431
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,560
Di,

432
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:44,960
I've heard Jiangnan Circuit
is a strange place.

433
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:47,080
There have been bizarre cases

434
00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:48,120
involving demons and ghosts.

435
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:50,840
Her Highness is sending you
straight into the lion's den.

436
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:51,960
Master,

437
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,680
she's deliberately setting a trap
for you.

438
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,640
No evil force, however sinister,

439
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,680
can surpass the treachery
of the human heart.

440
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,320
No challenge, however difficult,

441
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:01,560
can withstand the power of justice.

442
00:22:04,140 --> 00:22:07,140
(Shendu)

443
00:22:10,900 --> 00:22:15,220
(Ruanjiang County, Langzhou)

444
00:22:20,860 --> 00:22:23,580
(Second, The Ghost Letter)

445
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:27,120
Ruo,

446
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:28,680
I'm back.

447
00:22:40,700 --> 00:22:44,780
(Memorial Tablet
of Late Husband Qi Feng)

448
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:50,080
Ruo,

449
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:52,120
I'm back.

450
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:56,040
Qi Feng...

451
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:12,200
Ruo,

452
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:14,360
I'm back.

453
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:24,640
Qi Feng.

454
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,680
Qi Feng.

455
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:41,420
(Preview of Next Episode)

456
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,560
He was burned!

457
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:53,440
He was burned!

458
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,660
- What nonsense are you talking about?
- He was burned to death!

459
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,200
A water ghost!

460
00:23:58,920 --> 00:23:59,520
A water ghost!

461
00:24:11,390 --> 00:24:12,970
♪Night covers the long streets♪

462
00:24:14,050 --> 00:24:15,760
♪The city remains silent♪

463
00:24:17,150 --> 00:24:18,740
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

464
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:21,240
♪Words still left unspoken♪

465
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:24,280
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

466
00:24:25,410 --> 00:24:27,880
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

467
00:24:28,500 --> 00:24:29,980
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

468
00:24:29,980 --> 00:24:33,120
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

469
00:24:33,740 --> 00:24:35,660
♪Love is born from desire♪

470
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:38,480
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

471
00:24:39,620 --> 00:24:41,280
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

472
00:24:41,280 --> 00:24:44,580
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

473
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:47,350
♪Someone once warned me♪

474
00:24:47,350 --> 00:24:48,870
♪To stop upon this shore♪

475
00:24:48,870 --> 00:24:50,190
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

476
00:24:50,190 --> 00:24:51,680
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

477
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:52,800
♪If one thought retreats♪

478
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:54,100
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

479
00:24:54,100 --> 00:24:55,440
♪But in this world♪

480
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:57,840
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

481
00:24:59,670 --> 00:25:02,480
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

482
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,950
♪Still I walk ahead♪

483
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:05,400
♪Let it pierce through♪

484
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:10,140
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

485
00:25:10,140 --> 00:25:12,380
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

486
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:13,780
♪Covering every heart♪

487
00:25:13,780 --> 00:25:14,970
♪How many people♪

488
00:25:15,230 --> 00:25:16,600
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

489
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:18,810
♪Yet call it♪

490
00:25:19,010 --> 00:25:20,350
♪Fate?♪

491
00:25:20,710 --> 00:25:21,890
♪Life and death♪

492
00:25:21,890 --> 00:25:23,150
♪Balanced on a single line♪

493
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:24,670
♪Light and shadow♪

494
00:25:24,670 --> 00:25:25,930
♪Hanging side by side♪

495
00:25:25,930 --> 00:25:27,410
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

496
00:25:27,410 --> 00:25:28,820
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

497
00:25:28,820 --> 00:25:30,360
♪In the end, it is only♪

498
00:25:30,360 --> 00:25:31,740
♪A single misguided thought♪

499
00:25:31,740 --> 00:25:33,300
♪If unveiling the truth♪

500
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:34,640
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

501
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,810
♪Then this answer♪

502
00:25:35,810 --> 00:25:37,170
♪Can it still remain true?♪

503
00:25:37,170 --> 00:25:38,570
♪When love and law♪

504
00:25:38,570 --> 00:25:40,050
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

505
00:25:40,050 --> 00:25:41,450
♪Which figure before me♪

506
00:25:41,450 --> 00:25:48,650
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

507
00:25:48,650 --> 00:25:51,380
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

508
00:25:51,380 --> 00:25:52,970
♪Still I walk ahead♪

509
00:25:52,970 --> 00:25:54,210
♪Not for fame or glory♪

510
00:25:54,210 --> 00:25:59,080
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

511
00:25:59,080 --> 00:26:00,890
♪Human nature is clouded♪

512
00:26:00,890 --> 00:26:02,610
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

513
00:26:02,610 --> 00:26:04,080
♪Though this world♪

514
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:05,450
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

515
00:26:05,450 --> 00:26:07,700
♪There is still a light♪

516
00:26:07,700 --> 00:26:10,660
♪Worth pursuing♪

517
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:12,480
♪Every case has its ending♪

518
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:13,740
♪But night does not always fade♪

519
00:26:14,010 --> 00:26:15,390
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

520
00:26:15,390 --> 00:26:16,610
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

521
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:17,960
♪If justice stands♪

522
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:19,210
♪Without mercy beside it♪

523
00:26:19,210 --> 00:26:21,010
♪Then how is it♪

524
00:26:21,010 --> 00:26:30,570
♪Any different from a blade?♪

525
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:33,760
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

526
00:26:33,760 --> 00:26:35,240
♪Still I walk ahead♪

527
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,630
♪Even if the world♪

528
00:26:36,630 --> 00:26:41,360
♪Refuses to answer♪

529
00:26:41,360 --> 00:26:43,320
♪When every hidden truth♪

530
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:45,030
♪Finally reveals itself♪

531
00:26:45,030 --> 00:26:46,390
♪I only wish♪

532
00:26:46,390 --> 00:26:47,870
♪To hold on♪

533
00:26:47,870 --> 00:26:52,610
♪Within the darkness♪

534
00:26:52,610 --> 00:26:54,610
♪To the heart♪

